{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3efc61769c","title":"上海工商界五反运动推迟开始　目前集中力量进行机关三反运动","origin":"新华通讯社编《内部参考》1952年2月29日","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4521cc1e41","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":27,"articleId":"3efc61769c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ad4d6c4420","type":"title","text":"上海工商界五反运动推迟开始　目前集中力量进行机关三反运动","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"3efc61769c"},{"id":"05b2582d89","type":"paragraph","text":"【华东总分社二十七日讯】薄一波抵沪后，华东局已决定将上海工商界五反运动推迟至三月底或四月初开始。目前将集中力量进行机关内部的三反。在机关内部现已发现不少重要线索，华东贸易部已发现一个虎窝集体贪污一万亿元。对工商界目前则暂采取稳定的方针：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"3efc61769c"},{"id":"6ceabf5a18","type":"paragraph","text":"(一)从今日起暂不抓人；","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"3efc61769c"},{"id":"7d878bd417","type":"paragraph","text":"(二)已捕者具保释放一批；","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"3efc61769c"},{"id":"9990475357","type":"paragraph","text":"(三)搜集研究各方检举材料；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"3efc61769c"},{"id":"cbcf77d991","type":"paragraph","text":"(四)报纸除一般揭露资产阶级丑恶外，逐渐将火力转向内部三反；","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"3efc61769c"},{"id":"3985513a89","type":"paragraph","text":"(五)店员打锣打鼓的宣传攻势暂时收缩一下。总之，先把内部整理好，然后集中全国力量最后在上海打决定性的围歼战。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"3efc61769c"}],"page":{"id":"62a06ff22c","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"3efc61769c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}